🚀 FlowSync — AI-Powered Productivity Landing Page

FlowSync is a modern and responsive SaaS landing page built using HTML and CSS.
The project showcases a clean user interface, advanced layout design, dashboard mockups, pricing sections, testimonials, and modern UI/UX concepts inspired by real-world SaaS platforms.

✨ Features
* Fully Responsive Landing Page
* Modern SaaS UI Design
* Sticky Navigation Bar
* Hero Section with CTA Buttons
* Dashboard Mockup Interface
* Features Showcase Section
* Pricing Cards
* Testimonials Section
* CTA Subscription Banner
* Professional Footer Layout
* Smooth Hover & Transition Effects
* Mobile Responsive Design

🎨 UI Highlights
* Minimal & Modern SaaS Design
* Elegant Typography using Google Fonts
* Soft Color Palette
* Interactive Hover Effects
* Dashboard Visualization
* Professional Card Layouts
* Clean Section Spacing
* Responsive Grid System

🛠️ Technologies Used
HTML5
CSS3
Google Fonts

📁 Project Structure
FlowSync/
│── index.html

▶️ How to Run the Project
Download or clone the repository.
Open the project folder.
Run the index.html file in any modern web browser.

